summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the improvement of S.W. Kenyon St. from 9th Ave. S.W. to approximately 130 feet east thereof and from approximately 130 feet west of 7th Ave. S.W. to 1st Ave. S.; and certain other street avenues, alleys and easements, by constructing sanitary sewers together with the necessary appurtenances and doing such other work as may be necessary in connection therewith, Local Improvement District No. 6683, and appropriating money from the Municipal Sewerage 1971 Construction Fund in aid thereof as a loan.
